ordic World Ski Championships 2009 \u2013 Women's team sprint|\u2014]]\n|-\n| [[FIS Nordic World Ski Championships 2013|2013]] || ''28'' || [[FIS Nordic World Ski Championships 2013 \u2013 Women's 10 kilometre freestyle|10]] || [[FIS Nordic World Ski Championships 2013 \u2013 Women's 15 kilometre pursuit|32]] || [[FIS Nordic World Ski Championships 2013 \u2013 Women's 30 kilometre classical|\u2014]] || [[FIS Nordic World Ski Championships 2013 \u2013 Women's sprint|\u2014]] || [[FIS Nordic World Ski Championships 2013 \u2013 Women's 4 \u00d7 5 kilometre relay|6]] || [[FIS Nordic World Ski Championships 2013 \u2013 Women's team sprint|10]]\n|-\n| [[FIS Nordic World Ski Championships 2015|2015]] || ''30'' || [[FIS Nordic World Ski Championships 2015 \u2013 Women's 10 kilometre freestyle|12]] ||  [[FIS Nordic World Ski Championships 2015 \u2013 Women's 15 kilometre pursuit|\u2014]] || [[FIS Nordic World Ski Championships 2015 \u2013 Women's 30 kilometre classical|\u2014]] || [[FIS Nordic World Ski Championships 2015 \u2013 Women's sprint|\u2014]] || [[FIS Nordic World Ski Championships 2015 \u2013 Women's 4 \u00d7 5 kilometre relay|8]] || [[FIS Nordic World Ski Championships 2015 \u2013 Women's team sprint|6]]\n|-\n|}\n===World Cup===\n====Season standings====\n{| class=\"wikitable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"4\" style=\"font-size:95%; text-align:center; border:grey solid 1px; border-collapse:collapse; background:#ffffff;\"\n! style=\"background-color:#369; color:white; width:60px;\" rowspan=\"2\" |&nbsp;Season&nbsp;\n! style=\"background-color:#369; color:white; width:40px;\" rowspan=\"2\" |&nbsp;Age&nbsp;\n! style=\"background-color:#4180be; color:white;\" colspan=\"3\" |Discipline standings \n! style=\"background-color:#4180be; color:white;\" colspan=\"4\" |Ski Tour standings\n|-\n! style=\"background-color:#4180be; color:white; width:75px;\"|Overall\n! style=\"background-color:#4180be; color:white; width:75px;\"|Distance\n! style=\"background-color:#4180be; color: