ao\n| Episode: \"Darkness Falls\"\n|-\n|2014\n|''[[Rosemary's Baby (miniseries)|Rosemary's Baby]]''\n|Roman Castavet\n| Miniseries\n|-\n|2014\u20132018\n|''[[Star Wars Rebels]]''\n|[[List of Star Wars Rebels characters#Grand Inquisitor|The Grand Inquisitor]]\n| Voice<ref>{{cite episode |series = Star Wars Rebels |serieslink = Star Wars Rebels |title = Spark of Rebellion |network = Disney Channel |airdate = 3 October 2014 |time = 43:07}}</ref><!-- was posted online on video on demand services prior to broadcast --><br />10 episodes<br />2014 BTVA Award \u2014 Best Male Vocal Performance in a Television Series in a Supporting Role - Action/Drama<ref>{{cite web |title=BTVA Voice Acting Awards |url=http://www.behindthevoiceactors.com/btva-awards/2014/television/ |work=Behind The Voice Actors |accessdate=1 November 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Dig (TV series)|Dig]]''\n| Peter Connelly\n| 10 episodes\n|-\n|2016\u20132019\n|''[[The OA]]''\n|Dr. Hunter Aloysius \"Hap\" Percy / Jason Isaacs\n|\n|-\n|2017\u20132018\n|''[[Star Trek: Discovery]]''\n|Captain [[Gabriel Lorca]]\n|11 episodes<br />[[Empire Awards|Empire Award for Best TV Actor]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/star-wars-last-jedi-thor-ragnarok-lead-empire-awards-2018-nominations/ |title=Star Wars The Last Jedi and Thor Ragnarok Lead Empire Awards 2018 Nominations |date=18 January 2018|website=EmpireOnline.com |accessdate=18 January 2018 |first=Ben |last=Travis}}</ref><br>Nominated\u2014[[Saturn Award|Saturn Award for Best Actor on a Television Series]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=Hammond |first1=Pete |title='Black Panther' Tops 44th Saturn Awards With Five; 'Blade Runner 2049' , 'Shape Of Water', 'Get Out' Also Score |url=https://deadline.com/2018/06/saturn-awards-winners-black-panther-blade-runner-2049-shape-of-water-get-out-1202418606/ |website=Deadline Hollywood |accessdate=28 June 2018 |date=27 June 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|2017\u20132018\n|''[[After Trek]]''\n|Himself\n|2 episodes\n|-\n| 20