-american-social-democracy|title=Bernie Sanders and the rise of American social democracy|newspaper=The Week|accessdate=26 March 2019|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite news|last=Dann|first=Liam|date=6 August 2017|url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/business/news/article.cfm?c_id=3&objectid=11898381|title=Liam Dann: Not another Jacinda Ardern column|newspaper=The New Zealand Herald|accessdate=10 November 2017|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite news|last=Day|first=Meagan|date=14 May 2018|url=https://www.jacobinmag.com/2018/05/bernie-sanders-workplace-democracy-unions-legislation|title=A Line in the Sand|newspaper=Jacobin|accessdate=20 July 2019|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite news|last=Debbaut|first=Karl|date=June 2007|url=http://www.socialismtoday.org/110/france.html|title=Has France moved to the right?|newspaper=Socialism Today|issue=110|accessdate=7 January 2020|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite news|last1=D\u00edez|first1=Anabel|last2=Marcos|first2=Jos\u00e9|date=5 January 2020|url=https://elpais.com/politica/2020/01/05/actualidad/1578218753_319107.html|title=S\u00e1nchez no logra la confianza del Congreso en la primera votaci\u00f3n|newspaper=El Pa\u00eds|language=Spanish|accessdate=7 January 2020|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite news|last=Demetriou|first=Danielle|date=17 October 2008|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/japan/3218944/Japans-young-turn-to-Communist-Party-as-they-decide-capitalism-has-let-them-down.html|title=Japan's young turn to Communist Party as they decide capitalism has let them down|newspaper=The Daily Telegraph|accessdate=30 October 2011|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite news|last=Digital|first=Milenio|date=12 December 2017|url=http://www.milenio.com/politica/descentralizacion-dependencias-amlo-presidente-2018-candidato-virgen-milenio-noticias_0_1083491829.html|title=\u00bfA qu\u00e9 estados quiere AMLO mover las secretar\u00edas?|website=Milenio|language=Spanish|accessdate=15 January 2020|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite news|last1=Dominiczak|first1=Peter|last2=Riley-Smith|first2=Ben|last3=Ross|first3=Tim|date=12 Se